casebody.data:
No. 10-746 (R46-016). Farhi Saeed Bin Mohammed, et al., Petitioners v. Barack H. Obama, President of the United States, et al. 563 U.S. 931, 131 S. Ct. 2091,

179 L. Ed. 2d 798,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 2821. April 12, 2011.

The petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the District of Columbia Circuit in the above-entitled case was dismissed today pursuant to Rule 46 of the Rules of this Court.
